metadata.name: AccountStatusesCleanupService #call when the account has posted several old statuses when called repeatedly with a budget of 2 reports 2 then 1 deleted statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT MAX(id) FROM (SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."account_id" = 111360527347950449 AND "statuses"."id" BETWEEN 0 AND 111281255022592000 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT 5000) t

SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND "statuses"."id" <= $2 AND "statuses"."visibility" != $3 AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM status_pins pin WHERE pin.account_id = statuses.account_id AND pin.status_id = statuses.id)) AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM favourites fav WHERE fav.account_id = statuses.account_id AND fav.status_id = statuses.id)) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM bookmarks bookmark WHERE bookmark.account_id = statuses.account_id AND bookmark.status_id = statuses.id)) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $4
SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."reblog_of_id" = $1 AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $2
